  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that spraying peppermint oil containing L-menthol onto the
      colonic mucosa during colonoscopy will relax smooth muscle allowing better colonic
      visualization.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
